title: Female Half-Elf Drow Sorcerer
description: Born from a slave mother, she has always had a penchant for power. She has always grasped for nobility and will do anything for that title, unless it caused her best friend to be in danger.

title: Male Kenku Ranger
description: Alone most of his life, he never learned to communicate. Watching from afar, he learned how to survive with the bow and learned of his fascination with fabrics.

title: Male Tortle Paladin
description: Rescued from near death, he started paying attention to the teachings of the deity worshipped by his rescuer. He now travels through the land doing good and mentoring the young ones in ways of truth.

title: Female Halfling Druid
description: Carefree and full of love of nature, this halfling finds her home in the wilds of the Sword Coast. Playing with animals in her animal forms, there isn't a thing she would rather be doing.

title: Male Halfling Ranger
description: A self proclaimed dragon hunter, he spends his time hunting the dragons that destroyed his village with the help of his faithful panther companion.

title: Male Dwarven Wizard
description: He found his spellbook pages in a mine he was digging and since then has a penchant for magic. Armed with the bits of pages and a hammer, this dwarf will stop at nothing to become what his oppressors fear most.

title: Male Gnome Artificer
description: Armed with his knowledge of the arcane and a screwdriver, their is nothing that this little guy can't build (that includes his hulking bodyguard).

title: Male Kenku Cleric
description: Armed with a spear and his faith in the Raven Queen, this little cleric will become the tool he needs to be. Assembled with a motley crew, he will be able to assist in all endeavors for healing, deceiving or sending people to the Queen herself.

title: Female Orc Barbarian
description: Once a slave to another tribe, rage built at the sight of innocence destroyed, she broke her bonds and fled. Now with no tribe to call home, she roams the land in search of acceptance.

title: Female Tabaxi Monk
description: Trained in the sacred arts of the tabaxi tribes, this unassuming girl uses her slight appearance to fool her targets in a sense of superiority until she strikes.
